OL,3,CThe community aiming to raise millions
OL,4,Cto bring derelict cottages back to life
OL,6,FSam Blackledge takes a look inside
OL,7,Fabandoned cottages in Looe which could
OL,8,Fbe transformed for local people to
OL,9,Frent.
OL,11,FA project to save a group of abandoned
OL,12,Fcottages in Looe and turn them into
OL,13,Faffordable housing for local people
OL,14,Fhas moved a step closer to its goal.
OL,16,FThe former coastguard cottages, on a
OL,17,Fhill above the town, have been sitting
OL,18,Fempty for years. But now a community
OL,19,Fgroup is raising money to bring them
OL,20,Fback to life.
