OL,3,CThe community aiming to raise millions
OL,4,Cto bring derelict cottages back to life
OL,6,Fand are pushing for even more funds
OL,7,Ffrom local people who can buy shares.
OL,9,FSimon Ryan, from the Three Seas
OL,10,Fcommunity group, said: "It's a lot of
OL,11,Fmoney, but it's an old difficult
OL,12,Fbuilding.
OL,14,F"We've already got 1.6 million
OL,15,Fapproved and agreed, we're nearly
OL,16,Fthere. We need a quarter of a million
OL,17,Fin community investment. Local people,
OL,18,Fpeople around the planet, putting
OL,19,Ftheir hands in their pockets, buy a
OL,20,F#100 share, be part of this project."
