OL,3,CThe community aiming to raise millions
OL,4,Cto bring derelict cottages back to life
OL,6,FThere are currently more than 20,000
OL,7,Fpeople on the waiting list for social
OL,8,Fhousing in Cornwall.
OL,10,FKathryn Cobb, chair of the Looe
OL,11,FCommunity Land Trust, said: "There is
OL,12,Flittle if no affordable rented
OL,13,Fproperty in Looe. Probably only a
OL,14,Fcouple, two or three properties
OL,15,Favailable now, maybe #1,100 or #1,200
OL,16,Fa month, which is totally
OL,17,Funaffordable."JLocal resident Carol
OL,18,FGraham said: "I think it's just a
OL,19,Fbrilliant idea that a group like this
OL,20,Fhave got together to do something like
OL,21,Fthis.
